history.content: You should probably email the person teaching 375 directly.

I know that the 375 enrollment is being handled right now. I indicated on the form that I would rather do EE 375. However, I am in a situation where, for the class I am currently signed up for (Physics 7B) does not allow me to take CS 375 (which is why I signed up for EE 375), but a class I am on the waitlist for (CS 168), would conflict with EE 375. I only plan on taking one of the 2 courses (168 or 7B), and dropping the other. In the case where I get a spot in EE 375, but get off the 168 waitlist and drop 7B, how hard would it be to switch into CS 375?
